### Installation ğŸ”§

1. **Clone the repository:**
    ```sh
    git clone https://github.com/yourusername/sMadical.git
    ```
2. **Navigate to the project directory:**
    ```sh
    cd sMadical
    ```
3. **Install dependencies:**
    ```sh
    flutter pub get
    ```
4. **Run the app:**
    ```sh
    flutter run
    ```

